# Python Copy Cli Tool

Python Copy Cli Tool is a simple tool used for copying .txt files 
  from destination a to destination b.

## Usage

To show help do:
```
python copy_cli_tool.py -h
```

To copy file from path A to path B do:
```
python copy_cli_tool.py /file/a /file/b
```

Tool includes file extension validation. Only .txt files are supported at the moment.
